      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and spake unto the king of Israel, and said, thus saith the Lord, because the Syrians have said, the Lord is God of the hills, but he is not God of the valleys; See Gill on 1 Kings 20:23. ",
        "children": [
