      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "have said, The Lord is Cod of the hills, but he is not God of the valleys, therefore will I deliver all this great multitude into thine hand, and ye shall know that I am the Lord.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " [It was partly for the instruction of Israel, and to confirm their wavering faith in Jehovah (see ver. 13), that this deliverance was wrought. But it was also that neighbouring nations might learn His power, and that His name might be magnified among the heathen.] 1 Kings 20:28",
        "children": []
